<br>
While Playerauctions might benefit from the removal of the NO DROP tag, wouldn't the level restriction hinder them again? A person may be able to buy an item for real life cash, but they at least need to work up to a level to be able to use it. Just becasue they can afford it dosen't mean they can use it.<br>
<br>
I like the idea of losing the NO DROP tag but ONLY with the replacement if it with a level restriction.<br>
